Ecological notes : very common in broad-leaved, mixed and carr woodland; conifer plantation with broadleaved fringe, heathland including Breckland, dry and damp heath; moorland on granite; wetlands including water meadows,
Phragmites
, stream side and fens; old hedges; parkland; grassland; open montane habitats. iv–xi.
